         <abstract id="aspace_df97da25be39914dbc80c1f14a234880">The papers include sketchbooks of watercolor drawings and captions by David J. Piel depicting military and civilian life during World War II in the South Pacific; and related correspondence, memorabilia, and photographs.</abstract>
